{"id":291,"date":"2024-12-10T09:34:29","date_gmt":"2024-12-10T08:34:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/?post_type=wmx-projecten&#038;p=291"},"modified":"2024-12-17T11:20:20","modified_gmt":"2024-12-17T10:20:20","slug":"the-best-of-armin-only","status":"publish","type":"wmx-projecten","link":"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/project\/the-best-of-armin-only\/","title":{"rendered":"The Best Of Armin Only"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"bg-white padding overflow\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                                <p>The one, the only, the totally awesome Armin van Buuren played two amazing gigs at Amsterdam ArenA as \u2018The Best of Armin Only\u2019. Armin\u2019s largest solo-show to date in his home country, the Netherlands, additionally marked 20 years of an incredible career as a DJ and creative music producer. It was the first time a DJ has staged a solo show at this venue.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-white padding-top\">\r\n    <div class=\"full-screen border\" style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/JLOUSBERG__D4_2327_PRINT.jpg')\"><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-white padding overflow\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                <h2>A VISUAL EXTRAVAGANZA<\/h2>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                                    <p><p>Creating an equally awesome lighting and visual design for the occasion were theatre designer Marc Heinz and Andr\u00e9 Beekmans of The Art of Light, who united the worlds of opera, drama and dance in a visual extravaganza to match the energy and diversity of the performance.<\/p>\n<p>All lighting was controlled from two GrandMA2 full size consoles (fully backed up) operated by Andr\u00e9 and Armin\u2019s long-time lighting director and operator on the road, Michael Seeverens \u2013 a mix of timecoded and manually triggered cues for the best of all worlds.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n        \n\n<div class=\"bg-white padding-top\">\r\n    <div class=\"full-screen border\" style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/JLOUSBERG__D4_3933_PRINT.jpg')\"><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-matte padding overflow\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                <h2>A FOUR-HOUR ACTION PACKET SET<\/h2>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                                    <p><p>The challenge was creating all the epic crowd-pleasing trance and dance looks over a four hour period and balancing these with the more precise and crafted lighting required for some of the soloists and aerial pieces. This is where the synergy between Marc and Andr\u00e9 works so well, uniting and crossing over two different base disciplines of lighting in this highly charged \u2018live\u2019 atmosphere. The four-hour, action packet set simply flew by.<\/p>\n<p>The Best of Armin Only: the best example for a next level light show and the ultimate experience.<\/p>\n<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n        \n\n<div class=\"bg-white padding-top\">\r\n    <div class=\"full-screen border\" style=\"background-image:url('https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/best-of-armin-only-8.jpg')\"><\/div>\r\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"bg-matte padding overflow\" data-parallax=\"move\" data-parallax-anchor=\"true\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-12-6\">\r\n                <h2>WANT TO KNOW MORE? CALL US<\/h2>\r\n                <p>info@theartoflight.nl<br>+31 (0) 40 780 5026<\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n\t\t\t        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":292,"template":"","meta":[],"tags":[11],"class_list":["post-291","wmx-projecten","type-wmx-projecten","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","tag-festival-events"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.1.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>The Best Of Armin Only - The Art Of Light<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/project\/the-best-of-armin-only\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"nl_NL\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"The Best Of Armin Only - The Art Of Light\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/project\/the-best-of-armin-only\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"The Art Of Light\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2024-12-17T10:20:20+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/best-of-armin-only-2.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1920\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"992\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\/\/schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/project\/the-best-of-armin-only\/\",\"url\":\"https:\/\/theartoflight.nl\/project\/the-best-of-armin-only\/\",\"name\":\"The Best Of Armin Only - The Art Of Light\",\"isPartO